MOTION DOCKET

97-1920. Gen. Dynamics Land Sys., Inc. v. Tracy.

Board of Tax Appeals, Nos. 95-A-443 and 95-A-444. On motion for admission pro hoc vice of David English Carmack and Donald B. Tobin. Motion granted.

On motion to strike portion of fourth merit brief. Motion granted and Sections B, C, D, and E on pages 2-10 are stricken.

Lundberg Stratton, J., dissents.
